Texas Chukwu, Abuja: In continuation of Chief of Army Staff operational visit to troops in various states. On Saturday 5 May 2018, at about 2330hrs- 1200hrs (11:30 pm – 12:00 am) four local armed robbers were intercepted by the Chief of Army Staff convoy along Numan – Yola Road. The robbers blocked the Numan – Yola high way, robbing motorists and passengers of there belongings. Items recovered include: 3 Dane guns, machetes, different kinds of charms. The suspects had since handed over to the Nigerian Police Force for further investigation and prosecution. The general public is hereby advised to always give useful and timely information to the security agency for prompt response. <img src="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai-315x420.jpeg" alt="" width="315" height="420" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62438" srcset="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai-315x420.jpeg 315w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai-113x150.jpeg 113w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai-768x1024.jpeg 768w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai-540x720.jpeg 540w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai.jpeg 810w" sizes="(max-width: 315px) 100vw, 315px" /> <img src="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai1-1-420x280.jpeg" alt="" width="420" height="280" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62440" srcset="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai1-1-420x280.jpeg 420w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai1-1-150x100.jpeg 150w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai1-1-768x512.jpeg 768w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai1-1-720x480.jpeg 720w, http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai1-1.jpeg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px" /> <img src="http://www.nta.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/buratai2-420x280.jpeg" alt="" width="420" height="280" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62441" srcset="http://www.nta.